OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775552356
OL,3,CTrump's Strait of Hormuz deadline
OL,4,Cticks closer as he expands threat of
OL,5,Cstrikes
OL,7,FUS President Donald Trump has
OL,8,Fthreatened to bomb all of Iran's power
OL,9,Fplants and bridges if Iran does not
OL,10,Fmeet his new Tuesday 8 pm EDT (1 am UK
OL,11,Ftime) deadline to allow shipping
OL,12,Ftraffic to fully resume through the
OL,13,FStrait of Hormuz.
OL,15,F"The entire country can be taken out
OL,16,Fin one night, and that night might be
OL,17,Ftomorrow night," Trump said. He
OL,18,Fsuggested that his latest deadline was
OL,19,Ffinal, saying he'd already given Iran
OL,20,Fenough extensions.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
