OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775552356
OL,3,CTrump's Strait of Hormuz deadline
OL,4,Cticks closer as he expands threat of
OL,5,Cstrikes
OL,7,FTehran earlier rejected a 45-day
OL,8,Fceasefire proposal and said it wants a
OL,9,Fpermanent end to the war.
OL,11,FIsrael piled on pressure by attacking
OL,12,Fa major petrochemical plant and
OL,13,Fkilling the intelligence chief for the
OL,14,Fparamilitary Revolutionary Guard.
OL,16,FTehran with its rejection, conveyed
OL,17,Fits own 10-point plan to end the
OL,18,Ffighting through Pakistan, a key
OL,19,Fmediator, Iran's state-run IRNA news
OL,20,Fagency said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
