CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775552356
OL,3,CTrump's Strait of Hormuz deadline
OL,4,Cticks closer as he expands threat of
OL,5,Cstrikes
OL,7,F"We only accept an end of the war with
OL,8,Fguarantees that we won't be attacked
OL,9,Fagain," Mojtaba Ferdousi Pour, head of
OL,10,FIran's diplomatic mission in Cairo,
OL,11,Ftold The Associated Press. He said
OL,12,FIran no longer trusts the Trump
OL,13,Fadministration after the US bombed the
OL,14,FIslamic Republic twice during previous
OL,15,Frounds of talks.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
