CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775552356
OL,3,CTrump's Strait of Hormuz deadline
OL,4,Cticks closer as he expands threat of
OL,5,Cstrikes
OL,7,FA regional official involved in talks
OL,8,Fsaid efforts had not collapsed. "We
OL,9,Fare still talking to both sides," he
OL,10,Fsaid, speaking on condition of
OL,11,Fanonymity to discuss closed-door
OL,12,Fdiplomacy.
OL,14,FAnd even Trump said negotiations with
OL,15,FIran continued.
OL,17,FActivists reported a new wave of
OL,18,Fstrikes on Tehran early Tuesday.
OL,19,FIsrael claimed credit but offered no
OL,20,Fimmediate details on what had been
OL,21,Ftargeted.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
