OL,3,CTrump's Strait of Hormuz deadline
OL,4,Cticks closer as he expands threat of
OL,5,Cstrikes
OL,7,FIt came as the Israeli military warned
OL,8,FIranians in Farsi on Tuesday to avoid
OL,9,Ftaking trains until at least 9 pm
OL,10,Flocal time, likely signalling a new
OL,11,Ftarget for its airstrikes.
OL,13,F"Your presence puts your life at
OL,14,Frisk," the warning, in a post on X
OL,15,Fread.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
