OL,3,CTrump's Strait of Hormuz deadline
OL,4,Cticks closer as he expands threat of
OL,5,Cstrikes
OL,7,FTrump has issued ultimatums to Iran
OL,8,Fbefore, only to find ways to back off.
OL,9,FBut he was more explicit this time on
OL,10,Fplans to follow through.
OL,12,F"Every bridge in Iran will be
OL,13,Fdecimated by 12 o'clock tomorrow
OL,14,Fnight," he said, and all power plants
OL,15,Fwill be "burning, exploding and never
OL,16,Fto be used again."
OL,26,@vD@GO]wD@IOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
