OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775552356
OL,3,CTrump's Strait of Hormuz deadline
OL,4,Cticks closer as he expands threat of
OL,5,Cstrikes
OL,7,FAsked if he was concerned about
OL,8,Faccusations of war crimes, Trump
OL,9,Fresponded, "No, not at all." He
OL,10,Fsuggested that Iranians want the US to
OL,11,Fcarry out its threats because it could
OL,12,Flead to the end of their current
OL,13,Fleadership.
OL,15,FIranian citizens are "willing to
OL,16,Fsuffer," he said, "in order to have
OL,17,Ffreedom." But there has been no sign
OL,18,Fof an uprising in Iran as residents
OL,19,Fshelter from bombardment.
OL,26,@qD@LOUwD@VOUyD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
