OL,3,CTrump's Strait of Hormuz deadline
OL,4,Cticks closer as he expands threat of
OL,5,Cstrikes
OL,7,FInternational warnings piled up
OL,8,Fagainst expanded strikes. "Any attack
OL,9,Fon civilian infrastructure is a
OL,10,Fviolation of international law and a
OL,11,Fvery clear one," United Nations
OL,12,Fspokesperson Stephane Dujarric later
OL,13,Ftold journalists.
OL,26,@pD@[OUsD@PO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
