OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775552356
OL,3,CTrump's Strait of Hormuz deadline
OL,4,Cticks closer as he expands threat of
OL,5,Cstrikes
OL,7,FEgyptian, Pakistani and Turkish
OL,8,Fmediators had sent Iranian Foreign
OL,9,FMinister Abbas Araghchi and U.S.
OL,10,FMideast envoy Steve Witkoff a proposal
OL,11,Fcalling for the ceasefire and the
OL,12,Freopening of the Strait of Hormuz, two
OL,13,FMideast officials told the AP. The
OL,14,Fofficials spoke on condition of
OL,15,Fanonymity to discuss the private
OL,16,Fnegotiations.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
