SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775552356
OL,3,CTrump's Strait of Hormuz deadline
OL,4,Cticks closer as he expands threat of
OL,5,Cstrikes
OL,7,FIranian and Omani officials also were
OL,8,Fworking on a mechanism for
OL,9,Fadministrating the strait, through
OL,10,Fwhich a fifth of the world's oil is
OL,11,Fshipped in peacetime. Iran's grip on
OL,12,Fit has shaken the world economy.
OL,14,FTehran has refused to let US and
OL,15,FIsraeli vessels through after they
OL,16,Fstarted the war on February 28.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
