CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775552356
OL,3,CTrump's Strait of Hormuz deadline
OL,4,Cticks closer as he expands threat of
OL,5,Cstrikes
OL,7,FMeanwhile, Saudi Arabia has closed the
OL,8,Fonly road linking it to Bahrain on
OL,9,FTuesday after Iranian fired missiles
OL,10,Fat its oil-rich Eastern Province.
OL,11,FTehran's latest strikes came as
OL,12,FIranian officials urged youths to form
OL,13,Fhuman chains around power plants to
OL,14,Fprotect them, as the latest deadline
OL,15,Fset by U.S. President Donald Trump for
OL,16,FIran to reopen the Strait of Hormuz
OL,17,Fdrew closer.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/13
